parameters.name: Year
parameters.description: Spacecraft event year given in PDS time format (yyyy).

parameters.name: FDOY
parameters.description: Spacecraft fractional day of year (1.5 = Jan. 1 at 1200 SCUT).

parameters.name: HRANGP
parameters.description: Distance from Sun to spacecraft in km.

parameters.name: SECLAT
parameters.description:
Solar ecliptic latitude of spacecraft with
                        respect to true-of-date Ecliptic.

parameters.name: SECLON
parameters.description:
Solar ecliptic longitude of spacecraft with
                        respect to true-of-date Ecliptic.

parameters.name: HELLAT
parameters.description: Spacecraft solar heliographic latitude in degrees.

parameters.name: HELLON
parameters.description: Spacecraft solar heliographic longitude in degrees.

parameters.name: HILLON
parameters.description:
Solar heliographic inertial longitude of spacecraft with respect to
                        direction of zero heliographic longitude on 1 Jan. 1854 at 1200 UT.

parameters.name: REARSC
parameters.description:
Distance from Earth to spacecraft in AU
                        (used to calculate Earth Received Time - UT).
